text: In manufacturing, I brought back 700,000 jobs. (Obama and Biden) brought back nothing.

The Biden administration inherited gains of 50,000 jobs a month. We're now finally back to 500,000 jobs a month. We inherited a country where 4,000 people a day were dying from Covid. That's now down 75%.
The Biden administration has created more than double the number of jobs per month, on average, than any other administration going back to George H.W. Bush.
